Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.63,0:02:18.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 呐 美绪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.26,0:02:19.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.41,0:02:21.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前就很在意来的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.87,0:02:23.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么一直都是这个发夹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.37,0:02:25.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 这个么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.54,0:02:27.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知不觉的…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.52,0:02:28.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知不觉什么意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.80,0:02:30.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知不觉就是不知不觉嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.93,0:02:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,数学的笔记忘带来了…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.30,0:02:40.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧？今天有数学课么？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.60,0:02:42.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有啊 作业也有的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.26,0:02:46.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去取一下 你先走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.85,0:02:51.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 作业也没写 没有也一样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.57,0:02:55.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.07,0:03:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,selamat pagi
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.07,0:03:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs36}译注：印尼语早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.36,0:03:12.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了来了又来了 麻衣老师
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.32,0:03:15.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这难道是必杀——“不打招呼”么～？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.90,0:03:17.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是大型的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.59,0:03:18.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像山一样！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.88,0:03:20.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟 就像山一样！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.96,0:03:23.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 实际上不是山吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.74,0:03:30.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 看来不是山哪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.16,0:04:02.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我懂的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.99,0:04:06.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我懂的 麻衣你生气的理由…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.77,0:04:09.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为我昨天从麻衣的便当那——
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.55,0:04:11.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿了一块西兰花吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.95,0:04:13.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这么想的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.08,0:04:16.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以买来啦 西兰花！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.60,0:04:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 吃下去之后就立刻想起来麻衣喜欢吃西兰花来的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.40,0:04:23.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从那之后就一直觉得很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.43,0:04:25.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此 给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.54,0:04:37.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来不是因为西兰花
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.37,0:04:40.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菜花？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.15,0:04:42.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.44,0:04:58.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔 干的蠢事太多了 根本不知道她为哪件事生气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.70,0:05:04.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是总算是有个大体的方向
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.57,0:05:07.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不想一直都这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.02,0:05:11.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话 只能老老实实的道歉！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.92,0:05:16.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.87,0:05:18.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿了你昨天的主食（汉堡）真抱歉！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.51,0:05:20.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\frz24\pos(431,483)\bord1\shad1\c&H2B3786&\3c&H13152B&\4c&H6DCDE6&}买的实惠
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.51,0:05:20.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\bord1\shad1\c&H2B3786&\3c&H13152B&\4c&H6DCDE6&\pos(738,527)}标价打七折
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.51,0:05:20.26,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18\pos(777,422)}碎猪肉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.51,0:05:20.26,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs15\pos(860,405)}澳大利亚产
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.87,0:05:24.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿了你的兔子对不起！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.86,0:05:25.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃了你的米饭对不起！！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.23,0:05:27.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑豆剩下了对不起！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.43,0:05:31.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事 为什么那么生气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.52,0:05:34.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经不知道了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.52,0:05:36.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是昨天白天的事么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.42,0:05:40.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 难道是更往前的？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.64,0:05:42.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放在麻衣桌子上的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.28,0:05:46.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥勒菩萨的头被我折断了的事？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.43,0:05:50.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是说就那么随意拿出来的事？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.71,0:05:57.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是说偷偷地埋到了土里的事？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.55,0:06:03.39,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\frz340\pos(539,332)}麻
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.55,0:06:03.39,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\frz340\pos(574,341)}衣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.55,0:06:03.39,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\frz340\pos(610,353)}抱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.55,0:06:03.39,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\frz340\pos(648,366)}歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.55,0:06:03.39,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\frz340\pos(685,378)}啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.55,0:06:03.39,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\frz340\pos(721,390)}☆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.78,0:06:00.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后还是重新考虑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.18,0:06:02.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都收好了放在麻衣的桌子上的事？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.22,0:06:05.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又重新考虑了一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.73,0:06:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在焚烧炉里面烧了的事？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.26,0:06:10.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 麻衣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.11,0:06:22.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.63,0:06:26.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 听着音乐呢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.65,0:06:28.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那确实是察觉不到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.04,0:06:33.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我连那都不知道 就好像在自言自语一样不停的啰嗦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.47,0:06:37.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好险啊 差点变成揭露自己的罪行了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.01,0:06:38.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后半段
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.92,0:06:39.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.24,0:06:42.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后半段 第一次听到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.91,0:06:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 田中君
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.47,0:06:54.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 可以占用你一点时间么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.77,0:07:02.28,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\c&H848484&\pos(411,478)}围\N棋\N子\N怎\N么\N了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.77,0:07:02.28,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\c&H848484&\pos(311,464)}足\N球\N怎\N么\N了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.15,0:06:58.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那个 那个发型啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.39,0:06:59.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 有点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.91,0:07:02.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变得符合风纪的话可不可以 什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.70,0:07:03.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.92,0:07:04.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.24,0:07:08.37,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18\frz7.809\pos(406,623)}站前
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.32,0:07:07.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,铜锣烧 吃么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.94,0:07:15.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完蛋了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.57,0:07:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全忘记有卷子了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.19,0:07:21.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离数学课还有 5分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.55,0:07:24.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美绪的昨天已经借过了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.64,0:07:26.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}一生的愿望！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.65,0:07:32.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开不了口…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.10,0:07:35.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里 还是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.16,0:07:37.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.24,0:07:40.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀妈呀 真是不好意思哈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.53,0:07:44.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,俺吧 数学的作业哈 有点忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.44,0:07:46.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那啥 要是行的话哈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.35,0:07:48.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能稍微让俺看看哈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.04,0:07:48.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.73,0:07:51.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 Thanks! 谢谢了啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.51,0:07:54.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微等一下哈 超快就抄完了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.85,0:07:56.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好了！ 迟大发了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.00,0:07:58.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好了！ 不好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.02,0:07:59.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你个蠢货！！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.64,0:08:01.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上开始你就很吵啊 正雄！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.69,0:08:03.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好了！ 迟大发了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.41,0:08:05.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这边是要被裁员了啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.07,0:08:13.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.02,0:08:15.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.68,0:08:19.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个好像不是数学的卷子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.42,0:08:25.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你喝果汁！！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.76,0:08:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.47,0:08:29.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.57,0:08:32.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上学迟到了 爸爸还被裁员了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.53,0:08:34.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪边都很严重啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.12,0:08:37.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该注意的才不是那里吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.89,0:08:38.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 这
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.73,0:08:41.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正雄危险啊！正雄会怎样啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.22,0:08:44.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.61,0:08:45.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪是这个时候啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.27,0:08:48.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪有工夫考虑别人的安危啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.25,0:08:49.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卷子啊 麻衣！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.06,0:08:52.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话 车站那边的那个也请你！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.39,0:08:53.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.62,0:08:54.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tha Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.75,0:08:56.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个 这个 就是这个哟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.14,0:08:58.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 这不是有嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.65,0:09:01.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早点拿出来嘛 麻衣你·真·坏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.81,0:09:03.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 把这个瞬杀掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.17,0:09:15.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我手里这张卷子 是什么时候的？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.79,0:09:22.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,900)\pos(652,493)\c&H0A0A0A&\shad0\bord0\K100}只{\K100}言{\K100}片{\K100}语
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.06,0:09:26.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想去新奥尔良
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.70,0:09:33.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 谁会这一题
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.87,0:09:36.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁都不会么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.57,0:09:40.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赤城的课真是处处都难死了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.90,0:09:42.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作业没写的话就会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.95,0:09:45.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问题答错了就会被训
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.16,0:09:47.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说在前头
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.09,0:09:49.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有干劲的家伙会立刻反映到内部报告里哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.01,0:09:53.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来这招啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.15,0:09:56.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种程度的威胁 不会那么巧的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.55,0:10:04.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.37,0:10:06.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是23日
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.43,0:10:08.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学号是23号的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.86,0:10:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs45}就是现在！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.72,0:10:09.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中之条！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.40,0:10:11.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 请假了么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.59,0:10:12.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.27,0:10:17.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抽筋了！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.70,0:10:21.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么偏偏这个时候手臂抽筋了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.24,0:10:23.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好办
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.26,0:10:26.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是这样的话 会进入他的视野！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.20,0:10:30.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 先去死角 死角 死…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.51,0:10:36.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs45}啊 怎么了怎么了 怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.03,0:10:36.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,椅子 先挪挪椅子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.81,0:10:39.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 谁的手机响了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.64,0:10:43.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感谢你的来电
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.23,0:10:46.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,压轴戏么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.06,0:10:47.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,传奇！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.98,0:10:51.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,班上的同学们脸上的笑开了花
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.93,0:10:52.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.79,0:11:15.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么这个问题
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.01,0:11:17.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.17,0:11:26.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先出石头 接下来是布
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.69,0:11:29.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使出力量 石头剪刀布
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.47,0:11:31.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.75,0:12:01.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 砂糖和牛奶都买到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.07,0:12:04.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样一来没有忘买的东西了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.59,0:12:04.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs45}今天鸡蛋好便宜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.67,0:12:10.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs45}我也买了不少 真实惠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.15,0:12:09.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.03,0:12:12.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天有鸡蛋的特价的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.94,0:12:17.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办啊 还算赶得上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.80,0:12:19.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是再去一趟商店吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.73,0:12:26.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 黑猫先生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.23,0:12:32.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 好可爱！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.74,0:12:43.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 不能饲养啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.61,0:12:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有个博士
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.34,0:12:47.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.01,0:13:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.75,0:13:08.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.10,0:13:10.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 这只猫
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.61,0:13:11.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我抓来的！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.27,0:13:14.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以哦 随便带回来的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.86,0:13:17.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 但是很可爱哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.66,0:13:20.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛… 确实…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.79,0:13:23.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对 不是那回事！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.01,0:13:24.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 不可爱么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.12,0:13:27.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.11,0:13:29.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.09,0:13:32.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 要养宠物的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.32,0:13:34.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就要好好照顾的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.57,0:13:36.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士你能做到么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.21,0:13:36.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.04,0:13:39.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是什么都不做哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.73,0:13:42.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扫厕所什么的你也必须做
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.35,0:13:44.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名乃什么都不做么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.73,0:13:47.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就不～给你摸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.46,0:13:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔 那 那样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.20,0:13:52.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对 不是那么回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.17,0:13:57.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 博士博士
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.02,0:13:58.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡了哦 这小家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.48,0:13:59.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀 我来摸摸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.64,0:14:06.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 唰唰的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.46,0:14:08.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 博士你好狡猾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.18,0:14:09.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要来 我也要来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.88,0:14:12.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子也唰唰的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.96,0:14:15.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子两边也唰唰的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.46,0:14:17.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右爪唰唰的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.43,0:14:19.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左爪也唰唰的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.93,0:14:22.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尾巴也唰唰的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.80,0:14:26.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起尾巴 耳朵后面更唰唰的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.92,0:14:30.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 但是摸起来试试的话还是尾巴更…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.70,0:14:32.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尾巴才没有唰唰的呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.17,0:14:43.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.73,0:14:45.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是哪里疼么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.65,0:14:46.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闪光！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.55,0:14:48.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.59,0:14:49.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.82,0:15:03.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名乃名乃名乃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.04,0:15:05.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能说话围巾做出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.08,0:15:06.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦哦 博士好厉害 不如说好快
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.88,0:15:09.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶快给阪本带上试试
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.70,0:15:10.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阪本？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.06,0:15:13.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只猫叫阪本的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.56,0:15:15.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 箱子上面也写着呢嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.31,0:15:18.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样 真省事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.90,0:15:20.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.62,0:15:23.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能说话了呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.84,0:15:24.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要说了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.60,0:15:29.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好期待！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.00,0:15:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么想刚才也摸的太多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.40,0:15:43.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说 一般猫叫的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.88,0:15:46.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,几乎都是肚子饿了的情况哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.24,0:15:49.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 我们不太清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.79,0:15:51.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有名字！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.35,0:15:53.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因为箱子上写了个阪本
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.57,0:15:54.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也太省事了吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.79,0:15:57.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.45,0:15:59.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 我就跟你说了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.84,0:16:01.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.74,0:16:03.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们都多大了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.66,0:16:04.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,8岁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.90,0:16:05.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1岁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.08,0:16:07.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要是按人类的算的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.83,0:16:08.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经20岁了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.62,0:16:12.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该叫俺阪本先生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.58,0:16:13.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.66,0:16:18.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H522611&\bord0\shad0\pos(574,328)}大\N阪\N腔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.90,0:16:15.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,俺…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.05,0:16:18.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 接下来能白吃饭的话就多谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.34,0:16:22.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是要经常记得对年长的人持以敬意哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.15,0:16:25.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来顺便我想说一句 你们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.66,0:16:29.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要因为我是猫就狂摸我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.47,0:16:32.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说清楚的话 我倒不是讨厌被别人摸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.01,0:16:36.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是啊 猫也是有限度的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.82,0:16:38.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把他放回原来的地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.98,0:16:48.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.66,0:16:54.29,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(500,360)\shad1\4c&HF7F4F2&}草\N人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.28,0:17:14.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 请
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.07,0:17:16.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.42,0:17:18.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明在等着交房租 还送我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.90,0:17:21.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连食物都送我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.13,0:17:22.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以啦 可以啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.16,0:17:23.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,困难的时候就是要互相说明嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.27,0:17:26.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有什么需要的东西不用客气说出来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.04,0:17:28.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.62,0:17:30.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 那么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.18,0:17:33.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钱可不可以 什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.69,0:17:36.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊 不要稍微对你好点你就变天狗模样哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.69,0:17:36.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs45}译注：日语里用天狗形容自负、骄傲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.62,0:17:38.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.92,0:17:45.38,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\pos(500,400)\bord2\blur10}草\N人\N2
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.70,0:17:47.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教 教头 这是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.84,0:17:50.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你误解成什么了啊 校长
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.52,0:17:54.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,躯干的部分 开启看看？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.06,0:17:59.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs36\an8}译注：纳豆= =
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.42,0:18:12.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要是赢了的话 请你站前的那个东西就不算数了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.05,0:18:13.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.58,0:18:15.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.93,0:18:17.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 得手了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.35,0:18:18.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一盒果汁比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.95,0:18:20.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ready～ GO！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.67,0:18:27.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣 你刚才稍微耍了点赖吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.56,0:18:29.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是 美绪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.88,0:18:32.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实多少有点早了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.20,0:18:34.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有那么一点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.25,0:18:36.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 再来一次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.50,0:18:38.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那重新摆好姿势
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.79,0:18:40.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ready～ GO！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.86,0:18:44.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣胜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.27,0:18:49.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 大意了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.43,0:18:52.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,低估了对手的力量啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.30,0:18:55.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 这样一来热身也完毕了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.60,0:18:56.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 再来一次！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.42,0:19:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呀呀 这可是相当响啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.08,0:19:05.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天晚上通宵了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.78,0:19:08.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 但是 身心都热起来了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.17,0:19:10.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多要动真格的了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.39,0:19:12.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要开始了么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.98,0:19:17.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了啊 刚才在看别的地方来的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.33,0:19:21.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 连着大意了三次都被抓住了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.63,0:19:22.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕 好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.65,0:19:26.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小佑 差不多该…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.46,0:19:28.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 稍微等一下哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.82,0:19:31.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯 是是 原来如此原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.96,0:19:33.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 看穿了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.45,0:19:36.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新手运就到此为止了哦 麻衣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.64,0:19:38.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 堂堂正正的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.10,0:19:38.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs45}Ready
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.48,0:19:39.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切斯特！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.48,0:19:39.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs36}译注：刀语中咎错误口头禅的正确版本
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.56,0:19:45.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.83,0:19:47.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是挺有趣的么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.13,0:19:49.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个 是什么来着
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.35,0:19:50.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小佑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.23,0:19:51.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掰腕子是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.75,0:19:57.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美绪 这个拜托了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.59,0:20:01.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不可以 帮我保管一段时间
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.96,0:20:03.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久没有这么认真了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.68,0:20:07.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我差不多点啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.59,0:20:09.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那边不好好对待的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.69,0:20:11.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是也认真不起来么！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.00,0:20:14.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了 下一次要来真的哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.33,0:20:15.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要 使出必杀技了哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.44,0:20:45.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么 怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.62,0:20:48.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是莫名其妙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.07,0:20:50.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就说啊 不过是掰腕子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.61,0:20:53.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什么这么燃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.33,0:20:59.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更何况啊 我连想上厕所都忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.43,0:21:01.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先去一下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.63,0:21:05.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就觉着从一开始就好奇怪哟
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.83,0:21:06.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小佑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.92,0:21:11.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站前的那个和 23盒果汁哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.61,0:23:26.53,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}朝起きて　歯を磨いて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.61,0:23:26.53,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}早晨睡醒后 起床刷牙来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.78,0:23:29.53,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}あっという間　午後10時
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.78,0:23:29.53,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}不知不觉间 已到晚十点
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.91,0:23:32.83,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}今日も　たくさん　笑ったなぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.91,0:23:32.83,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}今天也遇到 很多欢乐事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.99,0:23:35.58,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}たくさん　ときめいたなぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.99,0:23:35.58,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}也有非常多 刺激与紧张
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.12,0:23:39.04,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}友達と　バカみたいに
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.12,0:23:39.04,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}和闺中密友 像笨蛋一样
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.21,0:23:41.96,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}騒いでる　時にも
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.21,0:23:41.96,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}大声吵又闹 偶尔会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.29,0:23:45.30,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}チラチラって　目が合う
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.29,0:23:45.30,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}偶尔瞥向你 四目便相接
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.42,0:23:48.01,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}…偶然、だよね。
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.42,0:23:48.01,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}这也不过是 偶然事件吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.22,0:23:51.47,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}初恋なんて言えない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.22,0:23:51.47,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}初恋什么的难以说出口
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.68,0:23:54.64,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}キャラじゃないんだもんっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.68,0:23:54.64,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}因为我不是这样的角色
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.81,0:24:00.64,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}ねえ　あしたも会えるよね？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.81,0:24:00.64,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}呐 我们明天 也会相见吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.89,0:24:03.73,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}まぶたを　閉じると
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.89,0:24:03.73,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}将我的双眼 合上了之后
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.98,0:24:06.94,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}キラキラ　キミだらけ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.98,0:24:06.94,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}脑海中只有 亮晶晶的你
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.11,0:24:10.24,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}今日も　楽しかったね
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.11,0:24:10.24,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}今天的我也 开心又愉快
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.40,0:24:14.66,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}あー　恋　してんだなぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.40,0:24:14.66,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}啊 陷入恋爱啦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.71,0:24:22.67,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}うれしいな　うれしいな
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.71,0:24:22.67,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}真的好开心 真的好开心
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.83,0:24:25.63,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}はじめまして　こいごころ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.83,0:24:25.63,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}第一次见面 我的爱慕心
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.96,0:24:28.84,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}あした　まだ　あえるね
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.96,0:24:28.84,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}到明天的话 我们又见面
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.09,0:24:31.51,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}おやすみなさい
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.09,0:24:31.51,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}现在晚安吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.22,0:24:36.26,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}ゆめで　すぐ　あえるね
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.22,0:24:36.26,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}在梦中很快 我们会见面
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.89,0:24:42.44,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,500)\blur3}おやすみなさい
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.89,0:24:42.44,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,500)\blur3}现在晚安吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.67,0:22:50.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天手臂抽筋了 卷子没做出来被骂了一顿
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.34,0:22:51.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太郁闷了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.43,0:22:53.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话虽如此
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.73,0:22:56.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣 最后正雄到底怎么样了？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.26,0:22:58.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.67,0:23:01.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真是的 我知道了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.45,0:23:03.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果汁会再给你买一盒的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.35,0:23:03.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.41,0:23:22.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能理解啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.08,0:23:31.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纳豆激□是装傻役 是不是想要吐槽
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.08,0:23:31.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs36}kinase：激□ 是纳豆中的一种功能因子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.94,0:23:34.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,激□是什么东西哦 还小夜曲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.07,0:23:37.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来 下一话的日常是 第四话
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.74,0:23:39.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敬请期待
